{"tid":1507047,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[尋釁滋事]麗晶花園兩居民被控擾亂公眾秩序罪","createTime":"2019-08-26T04:07:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T04:23:37.000Z","uid":58335,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c7e7a6bef382f9c8689619993c706326f21b9982","tid":1507047,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:07:08.000Z","msg":"想用呢條罪做港版尋釁滋事罪???<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】周日凌晨九龍灣麗晶花園，大批市民在保安部前理論，其中兩人被控擾亂公眾秩序罪，在觀塘裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n兩名被告分別26及35歲，由警車押送到觀塘裁判法院。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指，兩人周日凌晨在麗晶花園19座對開拍打警車車身和使用侮辱性言詞，被控擾亂公眾秩序罪，兩人毋須答辯。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官批准兩人以4000元現金保釋，其間要到牛頭角警署報到及遵守宵禁令。雖然兩人是麗晶花園居民，但不准在管業處十公尺範圍停留，以及不得干擾和騷擾保安員。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官將案件押後至10月21日再提堂。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=360475&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D360475%26refer%3D&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY0zY%2BUnkXQH0zW%2FJu7eEK44%3D&h=6ba5578b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D360475%26refer%3D&h=62ab2afa\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=360475&amp;refer=</a>"},{"pid":"ddfc0c32666704c93283e4c1a1205288d672eaf5","tid":1507047,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:13:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e1c95f9d26afa720a739011459038be047b23ca","tid":1507047,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:15:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3b1ba867f8b36531d23a3df385745bdea07d882","tid":1507047,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:15:55.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"66ddd51010d2c31cf5cfe327bff913888c30a557","tid":1507047,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:16: